data.title: KEQQ
data.text:
KEQQ-LP (88.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Grand Forks, North Dakota. The station is owned by the Grand Forks Bible Study Group. It airs an educational talk radio format.[1]

The station was assigned the KEQQ-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on February 10, 2014.[2]
